    "body": "Sounded straightforward so I tried this~ Currently have a working implementation, shows expected version if `engines.node` and current node version don't match, and if the variable is included in the module format. Not including the `$expected_version` variable in format doesn't change the normal rendering. \r\n\r\nWas thinking about adding an option to allow people to enable/disable it but if you don't put the variable in format then it won't show regardless? Just have to clean some stuff up.",
